name: Egon Schiele's Self Portrait (1912) By Zaam
description: The face filled with horror: the mouth half open, the eyes are wide. Panic has been channeled into painting, the agitation evident even in the way the pigments were applied. The sense of being pressed into a corner - a universal human feeling.  Originally created in 1912 by Egon Schiele, this NFT was put through artificial intelligence and manipulation to create a modern retelling of his brilliance.  This is a unique and single edition of 1
